parameters:
Omura: You know that part-time jobs are prohibited at our
school, right?
Hinata Aki: (Why did it have to be Omura who found out...)

Omura: Besides, your grades aren't exactly good either. If you
were to get a failing grade, it would be a violation of school
rules along with the part-time job.

Omura: The worst case scenario is suspension... no, even
expulsion is possible... And it would also cause trouble for the
club.
Omura: Geez... Such a troublesome student...
Omura: By the way, why did you need money, Aki?

Hinata Aki: The shoes I use for club activities have reached
their limit, so when I went to buy new ones at the store, I found
myself a little short on money...
Omura: I see... So that's what it was.

Omura: The teacher knows that you're passionate about the club
activities, so if you had any problems, I wish you would have
consulted the adults around you.

Omura: Alright, I understand! I'll pretend I didn't see what
happened this time.
Hinata Aki: Is it really okay...?
Omura: Ah... but I'm quitting my part-time job.

Omura: If there were reports from other students or teachers,
the teacher wouldn't be able to turn a blind eye.

Omura: ...That being said, Aki's academic and financial issues
are still unresolved, aren't they?
\NOmura: So, I have a suggestion from the teacher... Aki, you...
Omura: How about coming to the teacher's house to study?

Omura: And if you're willing to listen to a simple request from
the teacher, I'll even pay you for your part- time job.

Hinata Aki: (But... this is actually a pretty good deal, isn't
it...)

Hinata Aki: (Not only did they overlook my part-time job, but
this will also solve both my study and financial issues...)
Hinata Aki: I'll do it, Sensei!
Omura: Is that true?! Hinata Aki studying?!

Omura: Alright! Good deeds must be done quickly. Let's
immediately assess the areas you're weak in with a small test!
Hinata Aki: (Maybe I should have just quit after all...)

Hinata Aki: I've never studied this much before~ I'll probably
forget everything by tomorrow~!

Hinata Aki: Wow, turns out the teacher is actually a nice
person~ I thought they would be a mean teacher!

Omura: What a rude student. There's no other teacher who cares
about the students as much as this one, right?

Hinata Aki: By the way, what is the simple request you
mentioned?

Omura: Oh, by the way, the teacher has a friend who is a
painter.

Omura: The teacher really likes the works that their friend
paints.

Omura: But recently, that friend has been lamenting about not
having a good subject to paint...

Omura: It's sad that even as a teacher, they can't see his
works...

Omura: So... when I asked if there was anything I could do to
help, they said they wanted me to send them a photo of a good
subject, preferably a female.

Omura: So I thought, how about using Aki? You're active in
sports, so you have a slim figure.
Hinata Aki: Speaking of subjects for paintings... could it be...

Omura: There's no way I would tell my student to get naked,
right?
Hinata Aki: So, what kind of photo is it?
Omura: It's easy, just lick the vegetables a little.

Hinata Aki: Lick the vegetables...? Are you going to make a
painting out of that?
Omura: Oh yeah, artists tend to be eccentric, you know~

Omura: There are things that us ordinary people can't
understand.
Hinata Aki: Hmm... so that's how it is.
Omura: Is this camera position okay...?
Hinata Aki: (I'm getting nervous for some reason)
Hinata Aki: By the way, why the blindfold...?

Omura: He said that by hiding a part of the face, it stimulates
the imagination.

Omura: He said that he wants the subject's eyes to be hidden as
much as possible.

Hinata Aki: Wow... I don't really understand, but he's really
particular about it...
Omura: Then, let's have you lick the cucumber right away.
Hinata Aki: (I don't really understand what's going on)
Hinata Aki: (If I can get money from this, I guess it's fine)
Hinata Aki: (It's not like it's a nude drawing or anything)
Hinata Aki: Is this... mmm... the right feeling?
Omura: Ah, that's good... It feels nice...

Omura: (I can't believe I can capture Hinata Aki in this
state...)
Omura: You got this question wrong again, didn't you?

Omura: It's a subject that requires memorization, so if you
remember it, you can get points, you know?

Hinata Aki: I'm not good at memorizing~ It feels like everything
just goes in one ear and out the other!
Omura: It's all just mistakes because you're not good at it...

Hinata Aki: Ahahaha... you really know how to hit where it
hurts, don't you~...

Hinata Aki: But but! Thanks to Mr. Omura's teachings, my scores
on the past exams have been improving!

Omura: Indeed, your scores have been gradually improving. But
really... if you put in the effort, you can do it, so make sure
to study regularly.
Hinata Aki: Please go easy on me in my daily life...

Hinata Aki: That's right...! Thanks to Mr. Omura, I was able to
buy new shoes!

Omura: Oh, that's great! My artist friend was really happy about
it too.
Omura: By the way... I was asked to be a subject again.
Omura: If it's okay with you, Hinata Aki... what do you think?

Hinata Aki: Hmm~ It's totally fine~ It ended quickly last time
too~
Omura: Hehe, then... let's get started right away...

Omura: If I were to upload this image to the internet, I could
earn some money... And Aki is slowly starting to open up to me as
well...
Omura: (Don't rush, little by little... I'll make you fall...)
